[SPEAKER_01]: Well, I don't know other than to say that we just had six foot of snow, and you couldn't touch the tank with a bare hand.

17:31.415 --> 17:32.676
[SPEAKER_01]: You had to stick to it.

17:32.957 --> 17:34.118
[SPEAKER_00]: Right.

