[SPEAKER_01]: We went back to a little town called Sugar Town.

20:36.377 --> 20:41.403
[SPEAKER_01]: It was Sukerstop, and that's what they called their villages, were Stots.

20:41.423 --> 20:51.315
[SPEAKER_01]: And so we carried them up there, and we went back, of course, in the holding position, and we thought everything was over with and clear back there, but one morning,

20:52.105 --> 20:57.110
