[SPEAKER_01]: I knew that they were around that graveyard.

21:44.515 --> 21:49.602
[SPEAKER_01]: So when they, of course, they didn't come through the graveyard with my tank and I didn't go across the fence.

21:50.459 --> 21:53.924
